txt.en: Kyrstig has asked you to defeat the Angmarim cultists in Akhaldarâg tombs.
'We have to do something about these Angmarim cultists! They will raise every fallen dwarf in these tombs if we don't stop them... so stop them we must!'
Akhaldarâg is on the south-west side of the Pit of Stonejaws.
'Did you thin their numbers? Good! We may not be able to stop them by ourselves, but we must not allow these atrocities to continue!\n\n'The Angmarim will pay for this bold villainy!'
